{"tid":864284,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日地鐵故障 睇到晒00後係幾咁廢","createTime":"2018-10-16T05:40:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T12:18:36.000Z","uid":28762,"like":97,"dislike":840,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"567fbddca7e7cb6d4068026dad27b9fa220ecd88","tid":864284,"uid":28762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T05:40:34.000Z","msg":"我平時早開4個鐘返公司<br />\n唔洗同人迫丫ma <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁今朝照舊<br />\n起身 新聞都唔洗睇 <br />\n根本影響唔到我<br />\n返到去見冇咩人<br />\n仲黎左一次晨q<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n打打下 咁就黎到9點 有個大會要開<br />\n見大部份人都返齊<br />\n唯獨有個新黎00後 intern 未返<br />\n即黑 wtsapp 問佢係邊到 <br />\n知唔知今日開大會 你要幫手drop notes<br />\n隻00後夠膽死回 back in 1 hr <br />\n我即黑屌晒老母 限佢30 分鐘返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n順便要買埋杯咖啡俾我<br />\n佢答： ....ok tmb<br />\n<br />\n咁果然個會差唔多開完<br />\n佢先跑入黎 門都冇吼 拎住杯咖啡☕️<br />\n唔...唔好意思 遲左少少<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候我梗係黎了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 而家幾點 人地住上水 都8:59 返到 <br />\n你住金鐘夠膽死10:15 先返到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :地鐵訊號故..障<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 公司不嬲有睡袋提供 你唔識前一晚係公司訓？<br />\n跟住成班同事係到笑 知道我玩9佢<br />\n見到個00後開始眼濕濕 想駁又唔敢駁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  : dismiss 散會  杯咖啡都凍晒 la<br />\n跟手再一野整跌杯野 倒晒落佢條褲到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟手叫返佢返屋企洗褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n佢跟住咸撚到仆街咁走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e2cc52087d59c97baeecb42834b0d3d59bb140e","tid":864284,"uid":177422,"like":244,"dislike":1,"score":243,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T05:41:46.000Z","msg":